NK073(pu)002:1: // sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i lam rnam par bshad pa chung ngu bzhugs so //
NK073(pu)002:3: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje'i thugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK073(pu)002:4: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rgyud mchog las //
NK073(pu)002:5: skal macha ga dbang mchog lnga ldan pa'i //
NK073(pu)002:6: dam pa'i yul lnga mthong goms mthar //
NK073(pu)002:7: byed phyir mtshan nyid gsum brjod bya //
NK073(pu)002:9: 'bras bu smin byed rgyu dang rkyen //
NK073(pu)002:10: nus mthu can gyur bde gshegs rigs //
NK073(pu)002:11: yan lag 'byung ba'i gzhi ru dgod //
NK073(pu)002:12: de la sgrub pa'i rnal 'byor rgyu bshad pa //
NK073(pu)002:13: dbang po yul du snang ba kun //
NK073(pu)002:14: yul rnams yod pa ma yin te //
NK073(pu)002:15: kun gzhi rnam par shes pa nyid //
NK073(pu)002:16: dngos po sna tshogs par snang ba //
NK073(pu)002:17: dang po pa yi brtag gzhir rung //
NK073(pu)002:19: nges pa gsum ste thog ma'i tshe //
NK073(pu)002:20: so sor rtogs rgyu gzhung mthun pa'i //
NK073(pu)002:21: dbang mchog tshig yul byas la brten //
NK073(pu)002:22: phyes pas rgyu byas bsam rtog tshe //
NK073(pu)002:23: gzhung las grags pa'i gtan tshigs lnga //
NK073(pu)002:24: sngon 'byung rjes sogs las nyid dang //
NK073(pu)002:25: mi mthun mthun pa'i gtan tshigs gces //
NK073(pu)002:26: des na rang spyi'i mtshan yul la //
NK073(pu)002:27: bshes gnyen bdag po rim de thag /
NK073(pu)002:28: dang bas 'dod dang bag chags rgyud //
NK073(pu)002:29: shes rab spyan mchog rang rig nyid //
NK073(pu)002:30: gdod nas shes rab lnga yin mtshungs //
NK073(pu)002:31: zhes smos la sogs lhan cig byed //
NK073(pu)002:32: de dag sgo nas 'tshol byed pa //
NK073(pu)002:33: kun tu rgyu bzhin gdod smon byed //
NK073(pu)002:34: de yis gzung 'dzin spyod yul mtha' //
NK073(pu)002:35: yod med lung du ma bstan pas //
NK073(pu)002:38: 'on kyang gnyis rdzogs gnyis med don //
NK073(pu)002:39: kun yin gang yang min pa'i phyir //
NK073(pu)002:40: phyogs bral phyogs bdag bsam brjod 'das //
NK073(pu)002:41: thams cad mkhyen don bco lnga gcod //
NK073(pu)002:42: sems chos ye nas dbyer med phyir //
NK073(pu)002:43: brgyad drug shes pa shes rab mchog /
NK073(pu)002:44: nges pa nyid du rgyal bas gsungs //
NK073(pu)002:46: ngo bos 'brel phyir gzhi nyid nas //
NK073(pu)002:48: la la thun mong lam rnams nas //
NK073(pu)002:50: kha cig sems brgyad nas rgyud de //
NK073(pu)002:51: bskal pa zhing gi rdul snyed nas //
NK073(pu)002:52: thun mong mchog lam sbyangs pas 'phrad //
NK073(pu)002:53: thun mong sa mthar byas pa'i tshe //
NK073(pu)002:54: yang dag sku gsung thugs bco lngas //
NK073(pu)002:55: byin rlabs 'tshams par mos snang bas //
NK073(pu)002:57: tha ma'i tshe na gsung lnga yis //
NK073(pu)002:58: dngos ston sngon byung lam zhes bya //
NK073(pu)002:60: mos pa tha dad dbang gis na //
NK073(pu)002:61: bde gshegs sku lnga'i gsung tshul gyis //
NK073(pu)002:62: so sor 'tshams pa ra gtan la dbab //
NK073(pu)002:63: bskal pa gsum nas sbyangs pa yi //
NK073(pu)002:64: zab mo gsang thos bzod thob des //
NK073(pu)002:65: chos sku'i gsung gi tshul bzhin du //
NK073(pu)002:66: brjod med don gyis gtan la dbab //
NK073(pu)002:67: longs spyod rdzogs sku'i gsung lta bur //
NK073(pu)002:68: dgongs dang brda yis gtan la dbab //
NK073(pu)002:69: sprul pa tshig gi gsung lta bur //
NK073(pu)002:70: brjod pa'i tshig gis smel bar bya //
NK073(pu)002:71: mngon par byang chub gsung ji bzhin //
NK073(pu)002:72: rig pa'i rlabs kyis gtan la dbab //
NK073(pu)002:73: rdo rje sku yi gsung lta bur //
NK073(pu)002:74: gnyis med mtha' bral don gyis dbab //
NK073(pu)002:75: la la ngo bo nyid gsung ltar //
NK073(pu)002:76: snang srid mthong thos nyid kyis 'bebs //
NK073(pu)002:77: gsang ba'i sku yi gsung lta bur //
NK073(pu)002:78: spyod pa thabs kyis phebs par 'gyur //
NK073(pu)002:79: la la sngon 'byung bstan pa bzhin //
NK073(pu)002:80: ji bzhin don dam nges pa'i tshig /
NK073(pu)002:81: rang rkyen mtshan ma'i gtan tshigs dang //
NK073(pu)002:82: ldem dgongs sbyor pa'i gtan tshigs dang //
NK073(pu)002:83: bkri drong brgyud pa'i gtan tshigs kyis //
NK073(pu)002:84: so so'i blo la nges byed cing //
NK073(pu)002:85: brtags yul yongs su gzhig byed phyir //
NK073(pu)002:86: de dag las kyis gtan tshigs 'gyur //
NK073(pu)002:87: de na gtan tshigs dbang btsan par //
NK073(pu)002:88: gtan tshigs ma gyur gang yang med //
NK073(pu)002:89: de la re zhig tshig dbang du //
NK073(pu)002:91: dbab med ston pa'ang de yis de //
NK073(pu)002:92: mthong rnyed byed phyir dgos yod la //
NK073(pu)002:93: so sor rtog pa'i yul du 'gyur //
NK073(pu)002:94: 'tshol tshe dgos phyir de ltar nges //
NK073(pu)002:95: de la gcig shos thun mong mchog /
NK073(pu)002:96: thun mong grags pa'i rnam bzhi sogs //
NK073(pu)002:97: thun mong min pa rnam pa gnyis //
NK073(pu)002:98: tshig don mthun par 'bebs pa dang //
NK073(pu)002:99: gtan tshigs don tshig mi mthun pas //
NK073(pu)002:101: dang po tha snyad gtan la 'bebs //
NK073(pu)002:102: de bzhin nyid 'bebs ngag mnyam rtogs //
NK073(pu)002:103: bden bdag gnyis med la sogs pa'o //
NK073(pu)002:104: gnyis pa ci yang ma yin la //
NK073(pu)002:105: ci yang yin dang grub ma grub //
NK073(pu)002:106: de sogs don 'dod ci yang min //
NK073(pu)002:107: phyir yin phyir min phyir ma grub //
NK073(pu)002:108: phyir brjod gtan tshigs la sogs pas //
NK073(pu)002:109: mi 'dra ltos rgyu ngo bo'i phyir //
NK073(pu)002:110: de dag gtan tshigs 'gyur bar nges //
NK073(pu)002:111: de bas skabs 'dir de la brten //
NK073(pu)002:112: de de'i yul dang shes pa dang //
NK073(pu)002:114: med na mi 'byung tshul nyid dang //
NK073(pu)002:115: de ma grub pas de ldog dang //
NK073(pu)002:116: snang ba rang snang thabs chen dang //
NK073(pu)002:117: snang bzhin ma grub shes rab nyid //
NK073(pu)002:118: bar ma sems rtogs rnam par mthar //
NK073(pu)002:119: lnga bzhi gnyis sogs snga phyir 'phel //
NK073(pu)002:121: skabs skabs nyid du the tshom med //
NK073(pu)002:122: de mthar bzhi mthas gdeng ldan pas //
NK073(pu)002:123: dbyings dang rig pa gnyis med par //
NK073(pu)002:124: de bzhin nyid du rdo rje'i rigs //
NK073(pu)002:125: gzung 'dzin bral ba'i rang rig nyid //
NK073(pu)002:126: dmigs med tshul du rang snang ba'o //
NK073(pu)002:127: byang chub sems snang thams cad ni //
NK073(pu)002:128: shin tu brtags dka' gting zab pas //
NK073(pu)002:129: ma dmigs mi dmigs dmigs su med //
NK073(pu)002:130: sems nyid de ni ji lta bu //
NK073(pu)002:131: byang chub de ni sems yin no //
NK073(pu)002:132: sems dang byang chub gnyis med pas //
NK073(pu)002:133: sems can ma lus thams cad dang //
NK073(pu)002:134: dus gsum chos rnams thams cad yin //
NK073(pu)002:135: thams cad ma lus chos so cog /
NK073(pu)002:136: sems dang byang chub nyid du 'ub //
NK073(pu)002:137: yangs shing rgya che lhun grub ni //
NK073(pu)002:138: phyi nang snod bcud ye nas dag /
NK073(pu)002:139: dag rtog nyid kyang dbyings nyid yin //
NK073(pu)002:140: 'di ni rdo rje mnyam yin no //
NK073(pu)002:141: byang chub sems zhes brjod pa ni //
NK073(pu)002:143: rtog med rang rig kho na tsam //
NK073(pu)002:144: sangs rgyas sems can sems la gnas //
NK073(pu)002:145: mnyam pa'i don nyid ji ltar bu //
NK073(pu)002:146: mnyam nyid rang bzhin gang yang min //
NK073(pu)002:147: mnyam dang rtog pa gnyis ka med //
NK073(pu)002:148: thams cad lhun gyis grub pa dang //
NK073(pu)002:149: sgyu ma'i mig yor tshul shes pas //
NK073(pu)002:150: gnyis ka rang rig nyid du 'dus //
NK073(pu)002:151: chos rnams ma lus thams cad kun //
NK073(pu)002:152: rang bzhin ye nas dag pa yin //
NK073(pu)002:153: sus kyang ma byas ngang gis gsal //
NK073(pu)002:155: ye shes spyan gyi spyod yul ni //
NK073(pu)002:156: kun dang thun mong de ma yin //
NK073(pu)002:157: de bzhin gshegs pa'i spyod yul te //
NK073(pu)002:158: skyes bu blo rtsal rab kyis rtogs //
NK073(pu)002:159: thams cad ma lus gcig pa'i ngang //
NK073(pu)002:160: lta dang blta bar bya med par //
NK073(pu)002:161: ye shes sgron ma sbreng bas ni //
NK073(pu)002:162: phyogs bcu'i zhing khams thams cad mthong //
NK073(pu)002:163: thams cad ma lus don 'byung ba //
NK073(pu)002:164: tshig gis mtshon las gud na med //
NK073(pu)002:165: sgra nyid don gyi ngo bo min //
NK073(pu)002:166: don nyid sgra las gud na med //
NK073(pu)002:167: sgra dang tshig tu brjod pa ni //
NK073(pu)002:168: yang dag don gyi snying po min //
NK073(pu)002:169: ming tshig sgra la mi brten par //
NK073(pu)002:170: blo yis gting du go bar byos //
NK073(pu)002:171: dngos grub mchog gi snying po ni //
NK073(pu)002:172: dang po don rtogs mtha' mi gtong //
NK073(pu)002:173: chu srin phyag rgya ji bzhin du //
NK073(pu)002:174: skye bar bgrangs kyang lhung mi 'gyur //
NK073(pu)002:175: tshong dpon lam mtha'i bsam pa bzhin //
NK073(pu)002:177: shes rab dang po smos pa gsum //
NK073(pu)002:179: bar chad med sbyor shes rab rim //
NK073(pu)002:180: mtha' gsum kun 'gro mi g.yo dang //
NK073(pu)002:181: mthar phyin shes rab rim shes dgos //
NK073(pu)002:182: bdag nyid ma mthong shes rgyud ma 'byor bas //
NK073(pu)002:183: gzhan du tshol zhing sems can rmongs pa yis //
NK073(pu)002:184: bstan kyang ma thos mtshon kyang ma mthong bas //
NK073(pu)002:185: bdag dang gzhan du 'tshol bas 'tshang mi rgya //
NK073(pu)002:186: mi g.yo bkod pa bsrung bar rol //
NK073(pu)002:187: mdzad pa gnas stob rim don gnyer //
NK073(pu)002:189: dam tshig phrin las spyod pa dang //
NK073(pu)002:190: mchod pa dbang dang sgrub pa dang //
NK073(pu)002:191: phyag rgya sngags kyi lta ba rnams //
NK073(pu)002:192: shes chod bya yi tshig tsam min //
NK073(pu)002:193: de bas lam 'di'i bye brag mthong //
NK073(pu)002:194: thig le chen po'i rang bzhin la //
NK073(pu)002:195: bsgom pa rnam gsum dus gcig rdzogs //
NK073(pu)002:196: de nyid ma bcos mi g.yo'i phyir //
NK073(pu)002:197: de ni de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings //
NK073(pu)002:198: de nyid kun gsal ye shes phyir //
NK073(pu)002:199: de ni kun tu snang gi ngang //
NK073(pu)002:200: 'bras bu'i chos rnams kun dngos phyir //
NK073(pu)002:201: de ni rgyu yi rim pa ldan //
NK073(pu)002:202: rang rig byang chub dkyil 'khor te //
NK073(pu)002:203: thams cad kun nas 'khyil ba nyid //
NK073(pu)002:204: gzung 'dzin bral ba'i ye shes ni //
NK073(pu)002:205: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi gnas //
NK073(pu)002:206: gzhal yas khang dang dkyil 'khor dang //
NK073(pu)002:208: sems kyi cho 'phrul chen po yin //
NK073(pu)002:209: dam tshig dam tshig ces bya ba //
NK073(pu)002:210: gud na yod pa ma yin te //
NK073(pu)002:211: rang rig lta ba dam tshig yin //
NK073(pu)002:212: sdom pa rnam pa bcu gsum dang //
NK073(pu)002:213: spyi yi dam tshig mtha' yas par //
NK073(pu)002:214: thig le chen po'i ngang du gsal //
NK073(pu)002:215: bya ba med pa'i tshul gyis su //
NK073(pu)002:216: kun la thogs pa med par spyad //
NK073(pu)002:217: bzhi yi las dang gcig po yang //
NK073(pu)002:218: thig le chen po'i ngang du gsal //
NK073(pu)002:219: dngos por zhen bcom bdag dbang bsdus //
NK073(pu)002:220: bdud rgyas zug rngu gnyis zhi mthong //
NK073(pu)002:221: spyod pa rnam pa gnyis po yang //
NK073(pu)002:222: thig le chen po'i ngang nges phyir //
NK073(pu)002:223: gcig la mi gnas kun la spyod //
NK073(pu)002:224: spyod par byed dang spyad pa med //
NK073(pu)002:225: mchod pa'i rgyan dang longs spyod kun //
NK073(pu)002:226: bya byed gnyis dang las de yang //
NK073(pu)002:227: rig pa byang chub sems chen po //
NK073(pu)002:229: bdag nyid chen po'i ye shes la //
NK073(pu)002:230: dbang lnga ma btsal dus gcig rdzogs //
NK073(pu)002:231: thob bya 'thob byed thob byas pa'ang //
NK073(pu)002:232: rig phyir gzhan nas thob pa med //
NK073(pu)002:233: sgrub med spang med chos nyid du //
NK073(pu)002:235: thams cad gnyis su med pa la //
NK073(pu)002:236: bsgrub dang sgrub pa ga la yod //
NK073(pu)002:237: dper na sgyu ma'i cho 'phrul ltar //
NK073(pu)002:238: don du gnyer ba'ang chud par bya //
NK073(pu)002:239: brag ca'i sgra dang chu zla bzhin //
NK073(pu)002:240: sgra gzugs mtha' dang bral bar rtogs //
NK073(pu)002:241: phyag rgya chen po'i mtshan nyid ni //
NK073(pu)002:242: phyogs bcu dus bzhir gshegs pa yis //
NK073(pu)002:243: sku gsung thugs dang ye shes lnga //
NK073(pu)002:244: bdag dang dbyer med phyag rgya che //
NK073(pu)002:245: phyag rgya bzhin bcu gnyis po yang //
NK073(pu)002:246: thig le nyid las gzhan pa med //
NK073(pu)002:247: sngags zhes rab tu brjod pa yang //
NK073(pu)002:248: don dam kun rdzob dbyer med pa'i //
NK073(pu)002:249: mnyam pa'i dkyil 'khor chen po ru //
NK073(pu)002:250: sku gsung thugs kyi yi ge //
NK073(pu)002:251: de la sogs te bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK073(pu)002:252: rtag tu mnyam bzhag phyag rgya yin //
NK073(pu)002:253: dus gsum gting 'byin phyir sngags yin //
NK073(pu)002:254: rnam par phyed ba de dag kun //
NK073(pu)002:255: thos bsam brten pa las byung dang //
NK073(pu)002:256: chags pa g.yas g.yon lam las skyes //
NK073(pu)002:257: brgyud pa'i rnal 'byor las skyes pa //
NK073(pu)002:258: sa yi cha yis phye ba ni //
NK073(pu)002:259: nus pa thob dang ma thob kyis //
NK073(pu)002:260: mthong lam gnyis su 'gyur ba yin //
NK073(pu)002:261: zag yod ldog pa'ang gnyis yod de //
NK073(pu)002:262: mthu yis ngan 'gror ldog mi ldog /
NK073(pu)002:263: sngon gyi shes 'jug brgyad la yod //
NK073(pu)002:264: mthar shes 'jug la ga la yod //
NK073(pu)002:265: skabs gnyis mthar phyir rnam pa gnyis //
NK073(pu)002:266: yod phyir gcig la'ang gsum gsum ldan //
NK073(pu)002:267: des na spyi dang bye brag shes //
NK073(pu)002:268: gong gi don ltar ma rtog pa'i //
NK073(pu)002:269: blo ngan mnyam par khung byung nas //
NK073(pu)002:270: ma rtogs le lo snyoms las byas //
NK073(pu)002:272: sems kyi mnyam pa ma rtogs na //
NK073(pu)002:273: tshig gi mnyam pas 'tshang mi rgya //
NK073(pu)002:274: de bas don tshig ldan par byos //
NK073(pu)002:277: rnal 'byor rkyen yang rnam lnga ste //
NK073(pu)002:278: dkor bdun dngos nyid rang rig pa //
NK073(pu)002:279: don dam kun gyi rgyu yin phyir //
NK073(pu)002:280: lhag pa'i rgyu de dang por bsgom //
NK073(pu)002:281: bsam bya bsam par mi bya ste //
NK073(pu)002:282: mi bsam par yang mi bsam mo //
NK073(pu)002:284: de bas rang sems rtogs byas te //
NK073(pu)002:285: le lo g.yeng ba yongs spangs la //
NK073(pu)002:286: nga dang bdag med mnyam par bsrung //
NK073(pu)002:287: mnyam pa'i dam tshig 'bral mi bya //
NK073(pu)002:288: yid shes de bzhin nyid dmigs pas //
NK073(pu)002:289: ci smos tshogs brgyad spyod yul rnams //
NK073(pu)002:290: mi rtog gyur pos dus gcig gsal //
NK073(pu)002:291: de phyir thams cad mkhyen bsgom yin //
NK073(pu)002:292: de ltar rgyu la brten pa yis //
NK073(pu)002:293: gnyis phyir mtshams sbyor ting 'dzin bsgom //
NK073(pu)002:294: de'ang gnyis te phyag rgya dngos //
NK073(pu)002:295: phyag rgya shes mod dus min phyir //
NK073(pu)002:296: mi bsgom gcig shos rang rig la //
NK073(pu)002:297: sdug bsngal nyon mongs ngang gis med //
NK073(pu)002:298: kun tu rang gsal ye shes la //
NK073(pu)002:299: gnyis med don gyis gdung ba'i mchog /
NK073(pu)002:300: yongs grol las kyi skyabs kyis phul //
NK073(pu)002:301: de mthong de la zhen par bya //
NK073(pu)002:302: de ltar mthong goms su yod pa //
NK073(pu)002:303: gnyis la gsum gyi skye ba 'byung //
NK073(pu)002:304: de la brten pas don grub phyir //
NK073(pu)002:306: sems nyid yi ge phyag rgya dang //
NK073(pu)002:307: sku yi ngo bor rang snang phyir //
NK073(pu)002:308: 'bras bu rgya gcig spros bsgom pa'ang //
NK073(pu)002:309: sngon rjes gcig la goms byas nas //
NK073(pu)002:311: kha dog med pa'i kha dog lnga //
NK073(pu)002:312: gang rung nyid dam gtsor h'u bsgom //
NK073(pu)002:313: de la kha dog med sgo dbyibs //
NK073(pu)002:314: med pa'i thugs yig rang rig shar //
NK073(pu)002:315: brtan nas rgya gnyis rim brtan bya //
NK073(pu)002:316: yongs 'gyur rgya chen zhal gcig la //
NK073(pu)002:317: phyag gnyis yan lag tshang byas la //
NK073(pu)002:318: rang bzhin bab mchog bzlas pa bya //
NK073(pu)002:319: de goms drug la'ang de bzhin no //
NK073(pu)002:320: yang na mos pas khro bor bsgom //
NK073(pu)002:321: de yang de'i tshul bzhin bya //
NK073(pu)002:322: spyod yul drug nyid phyag rgyar bsdam //
NK073(pu)002:323: brtan na spros pa'i rnal 'byor la //
NK073(pu)002:324: zhi khro gang la sngon byas pa'i //
NK073(pu)002:325: zhal phyag grangs dang phyag rgya'i grangs //
NK073(pu)002:326: gsum dang lnga dang dgu rtsa gcig /
NK073(pu)002:327: dgu brgya la sogs zhal phyag dang //
NK073(pu)002:328: rigs gsum lnga dang bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK073(pu)002:329: rigs sam tshom bu'i grangs bzhin brlab //
NK073(pu)002:330: goms nas chu las nya ldang tshul //
NK073(pu)002:332: stong gi dkyil 'khor man chad du //
NK073(pu)002:333: rang rig gsal shar mthar phyin pa'o //
NK073(pu)002:334: stong khri ci smos tshom bu yang //
NK073(pu)002:335: shin tu bstan nas gnas khang dang //
NK073(pu)002:336: yo byad lnga sogs ldan byas te //
NK073(pu)002:337: sgrub pa dus kyi tshogs la sbyar //
NK073(pu)002:338: zla drug bcu gnyis bcu bzhi drug /
NK073(pu)002:339: khams dang brtson 'grus shes rab dang //
NK073(pu)002:341: dus der rnam smin lus de nyid //
NK073(pu)002:342: rdo rje'i lus gyur tshe la sbyor //
NK073(pu)002:343: mi ldog sa la nges par phyin //
NK073(pu)002:344: shes rab ting 'dzin ldan min pa'i //
NK073(pu)002:345: sman sngags la sogs tshe las 'phags //
NK073(pu)002:346: ldog bcas bzhi dang sbyor lam du //
NK073(pu)002:347: rdo rje'i lus su ma grub pas //
NK073(pu)002:348: rkyen gyi las kyis lus 'dzin na //
NK073(pu)002:349: spyod yul 'gyur tshe rang rig gi //
NK073(pu)002:350: rnal 'byor gsal byas stobs che bas //
NK073(pu)002:351: las ngan rgyun gcod 'brel ba yis //
NK073(pu)002:352: bde gshegs sngags dang bkor mi 'gyur //
NK073(pu)002:353: bshes gnyen dam mthong lam la sbyor //
NK073(pu)002:354: mdor na shes 'jug drug la yang //
NK073(pu)002:355: skabs kyis rgyu rkyen 'bras gsum ldan //
NK073(pu)002:356: de de der yang dgos ched gnyis //
NK073(pu)002:357: 'jug tshul gnyis kyis sbyor bar byed //
NK073(pu)002:358: spyod pa rgyun gyi tshogs bsags phyir //
NK073(pu)002:359: bdag dang gzhan don bsgrub bya pa //
NK073(pu)002:360: zag ldog mthong lam slob byed pa'i //
NK073(pu)002:361: spyod byed bcu mthar 'byin byed pa'o //
NK073(pu)002:362: rnal 'byor dang po dag phyir du //
NK073(pu)002:363: bya byed mi dmigs tshul la spyod //
NK073(pu)002:364: gnyis pa tshad med bzhi la rol //
NK073(pu)002:366: bzhi pa rnal 'byor spros la spyod //
NK073(pu)002:367: lnga pa dus kyi tshogs la rol //
NK073(pu)002:368: gzhan phyir so so'i rnal 'byor gyis //
NK073(pu)002:369: don byed ci smos dang po bcu //
NK073(pu)002:370: gzhan la ston cing bkri bar byed //
NK073(pu)002:371: spyod lnga mos slob ting 'dzin dngos //
NK073(pu)002:372: gnyis ka dbyings min grol bar spyod //
NK073(pu)002:373: dbang bsgyur thabs kyi spyod 'dra yang //
NK073(pu)002:375: de bzhin las bzhi tshad med bzhi //
NK073(pu)002:376: 'tshams par dus la spyod pa yang //
NK073(pu)002:377: shes rab ting 'dzin stobs kyis phye //
NK073(pu)002:378: bdag dang gzhan phyir spyod lam du //
NK073(pu)002:379: rnal 'byor rim bzhin spyod lam bsdam //
NK073(pu)002:380: longs spyod rnam drug rnal 'byor rim //
NK073(pu)002:381: mthun spyod rang grol gzhan mos gzhug /
NK073(pu)002:382: longs spyod bde ba'i bsod nams tshogs //
NK073(pu)002:383: zin chags bral ba'i ye shes mod //
NK073(pu)002:384: de de'ang sa yi zag dang sbyor //
NK073(pu)002:385: lam bzhis zag med slob par 'gyur //
NK073(pu)002:386: mnyan bsam mthong ba'i bsod nams dang //
NK073(pu)002:387: dbang dang rnal 'byor sgrubs pa dang //
NK073(pu)002:388: mchod dang phrin las dkyil 'khor dang //
NK073(pu)002:389: spyod pa kun dang tshogs gnyis te //
NK073(pu)002:390: spyod dang ma chags cha yis dbye //
NK073(pu)002:391: rgyu tshogs gdod mthar ldan par spyod //
NK073(pu)002:392: bdag phyir rnal 'byor grogs spyod pa'ang //
NK073(pu)002:393: spyod lam kun tu nyams mi bya //
NK073(pu)002:394: de nyid gzhan phyir sems yod pas //
NK073(pu)002:395: don du bya ba rnam gnyis rdzogs //
NK073(pu)002:396: de de de yi nus pa can //
NK073(pu)002:397: rnam smin tshe yi lus phye nas //
NK073(pu)002:398: lhag ma yod med lung bstan pa //
NK073(pu)002:399: mthar lam dngos la sbyor bar byed //
NK073(pu)002:400: phyag rgya gcig brtan 'pho ba yang //
NK073(pu)002:401: khyung dang seng ge ji bzhin no //
NK073(pu)002:402: spros tshogs skabs nas smos ci dgos //
NK073(pu)002:403: yid kyis lha yi lus brtan zhing //
NK073(pu)002:404: phyag rgya'i sku nyid gsal gyur na //
NK073(pu)002:405: lhag ma bzang pa'i bar ma la //
NK073(pu)002:406: de med phyag rgya chen por smin //
NK073(pu)002:407: las kyis lus sbubs rnal 'byor smin //
NK073(pu)002:408: ma rig cha la ming btags pas //
NK073(pu)002:409: smin pa'i ye shes lus su grub //
NK073(pu)002:410: rgya mig rgya sa lta bu'i tshe //
NK073(pu)002:412: sngon bzhin tshogs kyis dbang bsgyur rim //
NK073(pu)002:413: 'dzin spyad de nyid kyi grub pa //
NK073(pu)002:414: gzhan phyir bskal par gnas mod kyang //
NK073(pu)002:415: bdag phyir bcu drug tshun chad rdzogs //
NK073(pu)002:416: de tshe bsam yas lhun grub la //
NK073(pu)002:417: bsgom mthong stobs kyis 'jigs dang bral //
NK073(pu)002:418: shes 'jug rgyu rkyen stobs kyis skye //
NK073(pu)002:419: mthong nas gnyis med sku rdzogs pa //
NK073(pu)002:420: mthar phyin lhag ma'i lus smin te //
NK073(pu)002:421: ye shes sku lus nyid du grub //
NK073(pu)002:422: gzhan phyir smin dang sprul pa'i lus //
NK073(pu)002:423: thob nas tshogs chen sa la sbyor //
NK073(pu)002:424: kha cig dbang bsgyur rigs nyid nas //
NK073(pu)002:425: bcu drug rgyun gyi sku lnga rdzogs //
NK073(pu)002:426: kha cig phyag rgya chen po nas //
NK073(pu)002:427: bla med kun tu bzang por sbyor //
NK073(pu)002:428: rin chen bzhi yi rgya mtsho la //
NK073(pu)002:429: zho mar mi yi snang byed ltar //
NK073(pu)002:430: kha cig rnams gsum bgrod pa'i mthar //
NK073(pu)002:431: lhun grub rigs la rdzogs 'tshang rgya //
NK073(pu)002:432: shes rab dbang lnga rnal 'byor bdag /
NK073(pu)002:433: gzhi gcig slob pa bsam yas pa //
NK073(pu)002:434: rnal 'byor bogs la skabs ming brjod //
NK073(pu)002:435: mi ldog mi g.yo mthar phyin pa'ang //
NK073(pu)002:437: rtsal rdzogs tha ma'i sbyor zhes bya //
NK073(pu)002:438: bdag gzhan phyir na spyod pa lnga //
NK073(pu)002:439: tshad med la sogs spyad pa rnams //
NK073(pu)002:440: mi gos mod kyang sgrib pa gsum //
NK073(pu)002:441: gong 'og cha yig dag pa'i phyir //
NK073(pu)002:442: de nyid lam la khyad par 'gyur //
NK073(pu)002:443: yul dang nus pa mtho dman yod //
NK073(pu)002:444: de bzhin mngon shes spyod pa yis //
NK073(pu)002:446: rnam gsum yul dang zhing khams dang //
NK073(pu)002:447: byin rlabs la sogs khyad par 'gyur //
NK073(pu)002:448: bdag phyir yongs su ma chags dang //
NK073(pu)002:449: shin tu mi g.yo'i rnal 'byor spyod //
NK073(pu)002:450: ye shes rtsal gyi spyod pa yis //
NK073(pu)002:451: sa rnams yongs su 'phar bar byed //
NK073(pu)002:452: de yang dang po dang po dang //
NK073(pu)002:453: skal mnyam gnyis pa'i rigs mchog de //
NK073(pu)002:454: brgyad pa'i sems dpar skal ba mnyam //
NK073(pu)002:455: gsum pa bcu dang skal mnyam mo //
NK073(pu)002:456: dgongs spyod rgya mtshos khyad par 'phags //
NK073(pu)002:457: lta ba'i sgrib pa phye phyir ro //
NK073(pu)002:458: mthong bas ched du cho 'phrul ston //
NK073(pu)002:460: btsal ba med par cho 'phrul mdzad //
NK073(pu)002:461: de de de yis phye ba yin //
NK073(pu)002:462: de mtha' lhun gyis grub pa de //
NK073(pu)002:463: drug pa'i rgyal tshab skyes bu mdzad //
NK073(pu)002:464: gsang ba'i 'khor lo yang dag skor //
NK073(pu)002:465: kun la mthun pa'i gzugs ston zhing //
NK073(pu)002:466: mdzad pa bcu gnyis chos kyang ston //
NK073(pu)002:467: so sor thar pa'i lam yang ston //
NK073(pu)002:468: las rnams thams cad kun byas nas //
NK073(pu)002:469: skye shi med pa'i g.yung drung sku //
NK073(pu)002:470: des na mthu can rnam gsum po //
NK073(pu)002:471: sprul pa longs spyod drug pa la //
NK073(pu)002:472: rim par zhal mthong kan mod kyang //
NK073(pu)002:473: gcig gi ston par gcig 'gyur bas //
NK073(pu)002:474: rim pa bzhin du blar gyur te //
NK073(pu)002:475: khyad pa che ba de ltar yang //
NK073(pu)002:476: skabs nas rdzogs sangs rgyas 'gyur ba //
NK073(pu)002:477: rgyu dang dgos dgongs dbang phye ba //
NK073(pu)002:478: khyad par med snang de 'dra la //
NK073(pu)002:479: de phyir mnyam par lta ma yin //
NK073(pu)002:480: de ltar rnams gsum gang zhig la //
NK073(pu)002:481: thams cad mkhyen pa mngon byas pas //
NK073(pu)002:482: rang bzhin lhun grub dkyil 'khor du //
NK073(pu)002:483: ye shes lha mo rol dbang gis //
NK073(pu)002:484: seng ge lta bu'i gsung go bas //
NK073(pu)002:485: dngos po rang byung ye shes myong //
NK073(pu)002:486: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i spyi gzugs can //
NK073(pu)002:487: sku gsung thugs lnga rdzogs pa des //
NK073(pu)002:488: byin rlabs 'byin dang bstan pa'i phyir //
NK073(pu)002:489: lnga gsum kun gyis brtan par zad //
NK073(pu)002:490: de phyir mun pa rnam gnyis so //
NK073(pu)002:491: rnal 'byor ye shes stobs dang ni //
NK073(pu)002:492: rim pa thob pa'i stobs bcom pas //
NK073(pu)002:493: sa pa'i ye shes phyogs bral rgyas //
NK073(pu)002:494: sku gsung thugs dang yon tan las //
NK073(pu)002:495: ngo mtshar 'bras bu gzhan med de //
NK073(pu)002:496: thabs la brten pa'i shes rab nyid //
NK073(pu)002:497: de lta bu yi ngang du 'byung //
NK073(pu)002:498: spyod yul bral bas ma chags phyir //
NK073(pu)002:499: chu skyes can gyi sa yang thob //
NK073(pu)002:500: phung sogs rang bzhin dkyil 'khor der //
NK073(pu)002:501: mngon byas tshogs chen sa yang rdzogs //
NK073(pu)002:502: de nyid rang byung 'od gsal ba //
NK073(pu)002:503: mngon gyur ye shes bla ma'o //
NK073(pu)002:504: kun gzhi ma bcos mngon byas phyir //
NK073(pu)002:505: de bzhin nyid du gshegs pa yang //
NK073(pu)002:506: drug 'gro brgyad rgyud tha dad kyang //
NK073(pu)002:507: rigs rgyud min phyir shin tu gcig /
NK073(pu)002:508: gcig po ma 'dres yongs rdzogs pas //
NK073(pu)002:509: thams cad mkhyen nyid bsam yas kyang //
NK073(pu)002:510: rang rig de bzhin nyid du 'dus //
NK073(pu)002:511: de nyid thabs chen ma 'dres phyir //
NK073(pu)002:512: gcig dang du ma bral bar gcig /
NK073(pu)002:513: rang sems lhun grub mtha' bral de //
NK073(pu)002:514: gdod nas cha shas gnyis med pas //
NK073(pu)002:515: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs snying po de //
NK073(pu)002:516: mngon byas 'dra phyir kun kyang gcig /
NK073(pu)002:517: dus bzhi sems phyir rgyun bral ba'i //
NK073(pu)002:518: gzung 'dzin bral ba'i ye shes ni //
NK073(pu)002:519: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi gnas //
NK073(pu)002:520: de phyir gnas der kun kyang gcig /
NK073(pu)002:521: sems nyid gdod nas chos sku che //
NK073(pu)002:522: de bzhin nyid kyi de nyid ni //
NK073(pu)002:523: dpag med sangs rgyas pho brang phyir //
NK073(pu)002:524: de ru kun bkod der gcig gnas //
NK073(pu)002:525: 'gro ba'i dus na rgyud drug nyid //
NK073(pu)002:526: rig rgyud mtshan dang gzugs ris med //
NK073(pu)002:527: de yang de phyir rgyal ba'i rgyud //
NK073(pu)002:528: gnas 'gyur cha gzugs ga la yod //
NK073(pu)002:529: 'on te thams cad gcig zhe na //
NK073(pu)002:531: dogs pa skye ba kun gzhi'i sems //
NK073(pu)002:532: gdod nas rang byung lhun rdzogs kyang //
NK073(pu)002:533: mtshan nyid mtha' bral bkod med pa'i //
NK073(pu)002:536: ye shes lnga'am rang byung gi //
NK073(pu)002:537: cha las btags kyi gzhan pa med //
NK073(pu)002:538: de phyir gcig mthar ltung ba med //
NK073(pu)002:539: rgyal ba de nyid rin chen ltar //
NK073(pu)002:540: kun gyi spyi gzugs yin pa'i phyir //
NK073(pu)002:541: rgyal tshab lnga la ris yod kyi //
NK073(pu)002:542: yang dag rdzogs sangs rgyas la med //
NK073(pu)002:543: rgyal ba kun kyang dus gsum chos //
NK073(pu)002:544: bdag phyir kun gyi spyi gzugs can //
NK073(pu)002:545: cha gnyis yod par gang gis rung //
NK073(pu)002:546: yod na bdag nyid chen po rdzun //
NK073(pu)002:547: 'od zer nyi ma'am shing me bzhin //
NK073(pu)002:548: ngo bo gcig la ye shes rgyud //
NK073(pu)002:549: so so yin na sprul pa yang //
NK073(pu)002:550: gdul bya gcig la mthun par snang //
NK073(pu)002:551: sems dpa' che dang khyad med 'gyur //
NK073(pu)002:553: gzhi don lung rig kun dang 'gal //
NK073(pu)002:555: de phyir shing gi me dpung ltar //
NK073(pu)002:556: ye shes ston pa bkri drangs phyir //
NK073(pu)002:557: rung gis yang dag nges pa med //
NK073(pu)002:558: de bas sangs rgyas yang sangs rgyas //
NK073(pu)002:559: log par rtogs brtags rnam dag cing //
NK073(pu)002:560: ye shes dbyings las mi gzhan phyir //
NK073(pu)002:561: thugs rje chen pos 'brel bas na //
NK073(pu)002:562: 'gro drug dus gnas ma lus snang //
NK073(pu)002:563: mtho dman kun gyi gzugs snang yang //
NK073(pu)002:564: bla med byang chub skur snang ba //
NK073(pu)002:565: me long lta bu'i tshul bzhin du //
NK073(pu)002:566: sna tshogs kha dog dbyibs su snang //
NK073(pu)002:567: chos rnams ma lus thams cad kun //
NK073(pu)002:568: byang chub snying po'i ngang nyid du //
NK073(pu)002:570: de phyir yul med thams cad mkhyen //
NK073(pu)002:571: dpag bsam shing dang rin chen ltar //
NK073(pu)002:572: rtog pa med par re ba skong //
NK073(pu)002:573: nyi zla chu dang gzugs brnyan ltar //
NK073(pu)002:575: sku gsung thugs kyi bye brag chos //
NK073(pu)002:577: thugs rjes 'gro ba'i sems la son //
NK073(pu)002:578: dus gnas kun la snyoms par zhugs //
NK073(pu)002:579: 'gro ba lam log lam stor zhing //
NK073(pu)002:580: dbang po lnga bral gcong rnying gis //
NK073(pu)002:581: zin phyir lam mchog sman chen 'di //
NK073(pu)002:582: bsdus pas mtha' yas rgyal bar shog //
NK073(pu)002:583: sgyu ‘phrul drwa ba’i lam rnam par bshad pa chung
NK073(pu)002:584: ngu zhes bya ba slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas
